{"type": "article", "id": 27290, "title": "日食壁灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-25T06:32:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702171502svJcqV3ahxH1zYpX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>觉得造型单纯模仿星体太乏味？不妨来看看这个能让你在家“观测”到天文现象的灯具吧。加拿大设计师 <a href=\"http://philippemalouin.com/\">Philippe Malouin</a> 最近为 <a href=\"http://www.rollandhill.com/\">Roll &amp; Hill</a> 设计了一款名为 Eclipse Sconce 的壁灯，通过简洁设计还原了神奇的日食景象。包裹在灯外部的是一个光滑的半球体灯罩，通过推拉下端的短杆就能调整灯罩与墙之间的距离，灯光效果也会随之变化。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.rollandhill.com/collections/philippe-malouin/products/eclipse-sconce\">购买链接</a>，售价为 950 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171500IV2qnE8YFW9PJNiG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0556701\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171500VgYHkaWn46iQKdyI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0556701\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171501IlnMSkh9ofF4RDpi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0556701\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171501XTPaOvDV9uWe6xlg.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56333333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}